  <div class="gallery">
    <div>
      <div class="heading">What did I build?</div>

      <p>
        I developed and deployed a self checkin kiosk for a medical clinic to support our virtual reception team at
        Advance Healthcare. This cloud-hosted app is used on iPads at several of our clinics, and the app interacts
        seamlessly with our practice management software to mark these appointments as "arrived".
      </p>
      <p>
        The interface had to be robust and intuitive enough to enable patients of all ages and backgrounds to use it
        effectively.
      </p>
    </div>

